OL,3,CHow this year's bad weather is
OL,4,Cimpacting tourism
OL,6,FAs families across the country prepare
OL,7,Ffor their first half-term break of the
OL,8,Fyear, hotel and holiday park owners in
OL,9,FDevon say they are hoping for a much-
OL,10,Fneeded boost after enduring a
OL,11,Fdifficult few years and a very wet
OL,12,Fstart to 2026.
OL,14,FAcross Devon and other parts of the
OL,15,FSouth West, it has rained for 40
OL,16,Fconsecutive days, according to the Met
OL,17,FOffice, adding yet another challenge
OL,18,Fto an industry already battered by
OL,19,FCovid lockdowns, the cost of living
OL,20,Fcrisis, rising taxes and storm damage.
