OL,3,CHow this year's bad weather is
OL,4,Cimpacting tourism
OL,6,FMany hospitality outlets say they are
OL,7,Fjust about managing to stay afloat.
OL,9,FHerve Regent, owner of a B&B in
OL,10,FBrixham, says he is hoping
OL,11,Fholidaymakers will choose to stay
OL,12,Fcloser to home this half-term.
OL,14,F"They don't need to fly to Spain or
OL,15,Fwhatever, it's actually not bad here.
OL,16,FI mean you can see outside there the
OL,17,Fweather is gorgeous. And even if it's
OL,18,Fa bit colder, even if it's a bit wet,
OL,19,Fit's just absolutely lovely."
