OL,3,CHow this year's bad weather is
OL,4,Cimpacting tourism
OL,6,FHerve admits the past few years have
OL,7,Fbeen extremely testing for the
OL,8,Fhospitality industry. He wants the
OL,9,Fgovernment to provide more support.
OL,11,F"We need more money. The Government
OL,12,Fshould first look after the B&Bs, the
OL,13,Fhotels, the waiting staff, we've got
OL,14,Fsome fantastic restaurants in Brixham,
OL,15,Fthey've got rates, but their national
OL,16,Finsurance has risen and everything has
OL,17,Fgone up. To actually make a proper
OL,18,Fliving, it's difficult."
OL,20,FClaire Fowler, at the Beverley Holiday
OL,21,FPark near Paignton, agrees.
