OL,3,CHow this year's bad weather is
OL,4,Cimpacting tourism
OL,6,FShe said: "It hasn't been easy, it's
OL,7,Fbeen very challenging over the past
OL,8,Ffew months, times are difficult.
OL,10,F"But there's a lot of exciting
OL,11,Fpositive things happening. We do need
OL,12,Fhelp from the Government on things
OL,13,Flike business rates and all those
OL,14,Fsorts of things, but there are lots of
OL,15,Fthings we can do to help ourselves as
OL,16,Fwell as the English Riviera BID
OL,17,Fcompany.
OL,19,F"It's about working together and
OL,20,Freally focusing on what is good."
