OL,3,CHow this year's bad weather is
OL,4,Cimpacting tourism
OL,6,FA spokesman for HM Treasury said:
OL,7,F"Smaller businesses like pubs and
OL,8,Frestaurants are the lifeblood of our
OL,9,Fcommunities but we know that they are
OL,10,Ffacing a difficult time.
OL,12,F"That's why this government is
OL,13,Fsupporting them with a #4.3 billion
OL,14,Fsupport package to cap big business
OL,15,Frate bill hikes.
OL,17,F"We are also backing them through our
OL,18,FSmall Business Plan, while capping
OL,19,FCorporation Tax at 25% and publishing
OL,20,Fa new High Streets Strategy later this
OL,21,Fyear to renew our neighbourhoods."
